name: Damayanti Quintanar
introduction: Mexican actress, studied in CasAzul, Artes Escenicas Argos. Currently based in Mexico City and fluent in Spanish and English, she's worked in leading roles in some of the most successful Mexican TV Series such as "Mujeres Asesinas" (2008) , "Terminales" (2009), "Pacientes" (2012), "Hasta Que Te Conocí" (2016), "El Cesar" (2017) and "El Secreto de Selena" (2018) as Yolanda Saldivar. She's combined her tv work with acclaimed theatre productions such as "El Gesticulador" (2009), "Las Relaciones Sexuales De Shakespeare..." (2012), "Sanchez Huerta" (2016) and "The Flick" (2018), and films like "Partes Usadas" (2006), "El Que busca encuentra" (2017) and "Como Novio De Pueblo" (2019), to name a few.
